parameters: Yui: "Phew~, the combatants today were a bit stronger."
Yui: "But, well, thank goodness everyone was rescued safely."
Yui: "Alright, I guess I'll change into my pajamas and go to bed."
Yui: "Polka!? Why are you in this room!?"

Polka: "Why, you ask? Because it's more comfortable than the
basement."

Yui: "I told you not to leave the basement because you'll be found by
my parents!"

Polka: "But your parents are on a trip for a month, right? There's no
worry about being found by others, so it should be fine to move around
as I like."

Yui: "Didn't I tell you that \n[6] is coming to stay for a month
starting today? Weren't you listening to me?"
Polka: "Ah, was that so? I forgot."

Yui: "More importantly, Polka... Today, I met some weird guys
different from the combatants. They said they were executives of
Zaidarg-G, but I hadn't heard anything about that."

Polka: "Oh, didn't I mention it? There are many enemies besides the
Dargnoa and combatants."

Yui: "Honestly... I'm doing your requests as a volunteer, so please
get it together. Geez!"

Polka: "Hehehe, but I understand. You're someone who can't leave
troubled people alone, a person full of a sense of justice."

Yui: "Now, Polka... You're going back to the basement. \n[6] is in the
next room."

Polka: "I don't wanna! Why do I have to go back to the basement
again!? It's dark and cramped and I hate it!"
Yui: "Hey! If you shout like that, the next room will hear--"

Yui: "You... you... you pervert!! Why did you come in without
knocking!?"

Yui: "Seriously, because Polka shouted so loudly, \n[6] saw me in an
embarrassing state..."
Polka: "So that was \n[6]... He's quite a good-looking guy."
Polka: "No wonder you have feelings for him, Yui-chan."

Yui: "Hey Polka, don't say weird things! \n[6] is just a childhood
friend, it's not like that at all..."
Yui: "Anyway, Polka... You're going back to the basement."

Yui: "Prepare yourself for the dark and cramped basement from which
you can't escape~!"
Polka: "Your words and your expression don't match..."
Yui: "Is that so~? Must be your imagination~"
